FW America On AlertPST Original Message From Brady Kevin Sent Friday January AM To Kulic SladanaAnna Pehlivanova Biliana Ames Chuck Darren Espey Email Greg Watson Email Choate Heather Hernandez Jesus A Josh Harding Email Martin McDonald Email NDBrady Email Pimenov Vladi Subject FW America On Alert Original Message From Gilmore Tammy Sent Friday January AM Subject FW America On Alert A LITTLE AFTERNOON HUMOR Stay on alert Weve been advised that terrorists may attempt to pass themselves off as ordinary American citizens and may even attempt to change their hair color wardrobe or appearance in order to blend in You are advised to notify the authorities of any suspicious individuals who may match the following examples See attached file Example

AnalystAssociate ProgramDear Mr Lavorato I am writing you to express my dissapointment about how the whole AA issue with UBS was handled I have been working for a year as an Analyst in the Gas Risk Management Group In that period I learned a lot about risk and trading and eventhough sometimes we worked crazy hours I thought I had this incredible job and I worked with the best people in the industry How few of us get a chance like that I was looking forward to my next rotation in the origination group when the whole Enron scandal started happening Even when we filed the bankruptcy I still knew that the trading group will survive and I was right But I never thought that the management will so easily forget about the analysts and not even try to negotiate analysts salaries with UBS that all of us knew were the lowest in the market And I am completely sure UBS knew that too but why would they pay us more when our own management did not stand behind us I remember the times when I was working till pm or sometimes even longer but since I had this incredible group of people to work with I always thought someone would recognize that But it looks like that it does not matter anymore how much you work but who do you know Mr Lavorato I wanted to share this with you because I know that you can make a difference and that you always cared about the AA program Eventhough it may be late for me it would be a great loss for the company if all these smart people start leaving Many of them are the brightest individuals I ever met and I think they are the future of UBS Trading Group I hope that you will at least think about what I said because I know that you have a lot on your mind I wish you a lot of success in this year Sincerely Anna Kulic Gas Risk Management
